{"tid":1945874,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"因應疫情坂本龍音樂會提供免費直播","createTime":"2020-03-27T10:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T13:14:22.000Z","uid":12836,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f059f16cb62a977824216d1fbc22c8d4ec660bd","tid":1945874,"uid":12836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T10:14:21.000Z","msg":"坂本龍一與其他音樂家合作的「commmons」計劃，今日在Facebook宣佈將與三味線演奏家本條秀慈郎，在香港時間 4 月 2  日晚上 6 點，舉辦題為「Ryuichi Sakamoto: PTP04022020 with Hidejiro Honjoh」的音樂會。<br />\n<br />\n宣傳圖像寫有「不要輸給新冠肺炎！」和「緊急開催」等字眼，內文提及鑑於武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，各地政府呼籲民眾避免外出，減低病毒傳染風險。有見及此，是次音樂會將提供網上直播，全球樂迷在於 dTV 免費收看。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，大師一連四周公開「playing the piano europe 2009_Limited Edition」音樂會的錄像，全球網民均可免費收看。首條影像將於香港時間 今日（3 月 27  日）晚上 8 點首播，切勿錯過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N05KBgIEVQs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN05KBgIEVQs&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=e17d174f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N05KBgIEVQs</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/art/%E5%9B%A0%E6%87%89%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E5%9D%82%E6%9C%AC%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%80%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%9C%83%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E9%99%84%E9%80%A3%E7%B5%90/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%259D%2582%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E9%2599%2584%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25B5%2590%2F&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=c422d6b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%259D%2582%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E5%2585